{"tid":1901460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環海濱賣地政府話唔係價高者得！","createTime":"2020-02-27T23:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T01:11:23.000Z","uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e01d7410e65a91d03dd6002d1d0dcdbd2915988","tid":1901460,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T23:37:54.000Z","msg":"//政府公布下年度將推6幅商業地皮，共涉逾893萬方呎，其中以包括郵政總局的中環新海濱3號地皮最矚目，可建逾184萬方呎樓面，直逼同區地標商廈國金2期總樓面（約195萬方呎），地皮估值逾920億元，有力問鼎本港新地王。財政司長陳茂波日前公布新一年度財政預算案，預料財赤會持續數年，出售上述地皮能為庫房帶來龐大收益。另方面，政府表示中環海濱3號地將以「雙信封制」招標（見另稿），地皮有可能並非價高者得。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200228/s00001/1582828532078/%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e6%8e%a8%e4%b8%ad%e7%92%b0%e6%b5%b7%e6%bf%b1%e5%9c%b0-%e4%bc%b0%e5%80%bc920%e5%84%84-%e6%9c%80%e5%bf%ab%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%89%e5%ad%a3%e6%8b%9b%e6%a8%99-%e6%9c%aa%e5%bf%85%e5%83%b9%e9%ab%98%e8%80%85%e5%be%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200228%2Fs00001%2F1582828532078%2F%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%258e%25a8%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e7%2592%25b0%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%25bf%25b1%25e5%259c%25b0-%25e4%25bc%25b0%25e5%2580%25bc920%25e5%2584%2584-%25e6%259c%2580%25e5%25bf%25ab%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%25ad%25a3%25e6%258b%259b%25e6%25a8%2599-%25e6%259c%25aa%25e5%25bf%2585%25e5%2583%25b9%25e9%25ab%2598%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%25be%2597&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0fTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=62262c2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200228%2Fs00001%2F1582828532078%2F%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e6%258e%25a8%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e7%2592%25b0%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%25bf%25b1%25e5%259c%25b0-%25e4%25bc%25b0%25e5%2580%25bc920%25e5%2584%2584-%25e6%259c%2580%25e5%25bf%25ab%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%25ad%25a3%25e6%258b%259b%25e6%25a8%2599-%25e6%259c%25aa%25e5%25bf%2585%25e5%2583%25b9%25e9%25ab%2598%25e8%2580%2585%